item.title: CVE-2024-8234|2024-08-30T14:53:25.378Z -- zyxel -- nwa1100-n%20firmware
item.description: ** UNSUPPORTED WHEN ASSIGNED ** A command injection vulnerability in the functions formSysCmd(), formUpgradeCert(), and formDelcert() in the Zyxel NWA1100-N firmware version 1.00(AACE.1)C0 could allow an unauthenticated attacker to execute some OS commands to access system files on an affected device.
